{"tid":540894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大外牆凌晨被噴辱罵錢大康字句：屌你錢大康","createTime":"2018-01-26T02:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T02:54:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9b696bce291d397db4d5ace368e14ce5440941","tid":540894,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180126/s00001/df897357e452eb9cc25c0b7c5ae1d5a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180126%2Fs00001%2Fdf897357e452eb9cc25c0b7c5ae1d5a5.jpg&h=8428e348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180126/s00001/df9008ddde6dda461326ec05edbed260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180126%2Fs00001%2Fdf9008ddde6dda461326ec05edbed260.jpg&h=959aaf6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180126/s00001/df950c870bc03e7bf6bf414c462e9827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180126%2Fs00001%2Fdf950c870bc03e7bf6bf414c462e9827.jpg&h=7543fb95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180126/s00001/e1004f3da0946eca6ee0dcb11392b842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180126%2Fs00001%2Fe1004f3da0946eca6ee0dcb11392b842.jpg&h=2708665c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早7時許，警方接報指禧福道5號傳理視藝大樓地下外牆遭人刑毁，《明報》記者到場了解，發現字句已遭人遮蓋，據了解，今次不涉及粗言穢語，內容類似「反歧視NOPTH（不要普通話）」。<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學兩名學生被勒令停學，多間大學民主牆和其他校內範圍昨被發現有針對浸大校長錢大康的粗口標語，今天凌晨3時許，浸大區樹洪紀念圖書館外牆被人用藍油噴上粗言穢語「&times;你錢大康」，以及噴上「反歧視NOPTH（不要普通話）」中英文字句，暫時無人報警。"},{"pid":"94d68e4d734bf0a00754d0e0fcd5b47c3fc8d403","tid":540894,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5c7894d8e7244377da6f8a01a52a0d1f707904","tid":54